.Dd November 11, 2004
.Dt OSPFCTL 8
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm ospfctl
.Nd control the Open Shortest Path First daemon
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Ar command
.Op Ar arguments ...
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
program controls the
.Xr ospfd 8
daemon.
.Pp
The following commands are available:
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Cm show database
Show the entire link state database.
.It Cm show neighbor
Show neighbor summary.
.It Cm show interfaces
Show interface summary.
.El
.Sh FILES
.Bl -tag -width "/etc/ospfd.confXXXX" -compact
.It /etc/ospfd.conf
.Xr ospfd 8
configuration file.
.El
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr ospfd 8
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
program first appeared in
.Ox 3.7 .
